---
description: Forms and form state management rules
globs:
  - "**/forms/**/*"
  - "**/*form*"
alwaysApply: false
---

# forms.mdc

- Use React Hook Form for complex forms when appropriate
- Keep form state localized when possible
- Use meaningful validation messages
- Avoid duplicated validation logic
- Handle loading, success, and error states explicitly
- Prefer controlled inputs for complex interactions
- Keep form components focused and composable
- Avoid deeply nested form state
- Prefer reusable field components when appropriate